{"tid":576335,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一段深刻戀愛","createTime":"2018-02-28T21:03:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T21:29:12.000Z","uid":92669,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6e4f8928b4b756926675d8c816be3dc9c6de26a0","tid":576335,"uid":92669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T21:03:06.000Z","msg":"先寫為敬<br />\n<br />\n一直都唔信一見鐘情呢回事<br />\n直到嗰次去旅行，機緣巧合下識到佢<br />\n<br />\n個感覺好奇妙，一眼佢個剎那就已經定左終生咁，成個世界變左慢鏡，望住佢會有嚴重嘅淺境深。你會覺得咩都唔重要，只要同佢簡簡單單坐喺公園都已經好幸福。我諗咁樣就係一見鐘情啦。<br />\n<br />\n好好彩地，佢對我都係一樣<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻，發覺到戀愛原來係件咁幸福嘅事，好平淡都可以好甜。<br />\n<br />\n但最後因為預計到要長期異地戀，而無開始到<br />\n<br />\n你我雖然短短認識兩日，但足以令我記一世<br />\n<br />\n而家次次望返啲相都係傻笑然後好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31b12abd7f435eb2e7dbea63634c4152a706656","tid":576335,"uid":137669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T21:05:35.000Z","msg":"佢鐘意我，第一次感受到被愛係幾咁好，但我濫用左，最後放棄埋佢，而加好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0898eab380d078589211fcd1e54acaa3f18e98f6","tid":576335,"uid":131212,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T21:09:34.000Z","msg":"係佢教識我 除咗自己 邊個都唔可以信<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而事實上 係連最親近嘅人都唔可以信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37914dda1ca7502074ea4b5973691f2f3aa68b3","tid":576335,"uid":92669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T21:09:57.000Z","msg":"邊個A0負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb537bdf53a496c6f74482fd473d8c8e33accd8","tid":576335,"uid":92669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T21:11:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係佢教識我 除咗自己 邊個都唔可以信<br />\